data.name: label24.Text
data.value:
This agreement is between Delphina Hotel ("Discloser") and Customer ("Recipient"). The Discloser is providing the Recipient with an enrollment form containing confidential information. The Recipient agrees to keep this information confidential, not disclose it to any third party, and use it only for the intended purpose of reviewing the enrollment form. Confidential information does not include information that is publicly known, received from another source without an obligation of confidentiality,
or independently developed without using the Discloser’s information. Upon request, the Recipient will return or destroy all copies of the confidential information.
